Class BaseApiRequest<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yandex.money.api.net.BaseApiRequest<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApiRequest<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DocumentApiRequest, FirstApiRequest, Showcase.Request

    public abstract class BaseApiRequest<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ApiRequest<T>
    Base implementation of ApiRequest. It is preferable to extend your requests from this class or its descendants rather than create your own implementation of ApiRequest.

        protected void prepareBody()
